data.description: Welcome to this privately-tucked property, located in the quiet and prestigious Southwest Ranches community. It boasts a vast 2.5 acre lot with lush ackee, mango, and avocado trees, as well as livestock, and a natural pond. Home features tile flooring and a sleek metal roof w/the AC condenser recently being replaced. Ideal for those seeking luxury redevelopment opportunities or utilization of over 2 acres of land. The property includes a guest quarters with 1 bed/1 bath, a large garage, walk-in freezers, and a massive workshop—perfect for a variety of uses. Agricultural and homestead tax exemptions in place. Enjoy the added perk of being neighbors with one of the largest houses by living area in Florida. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your dream home!
